---
By: Maggid of Merzeritch
Source:
  ISBN: 978-1571746931
  Locus:
    Page: 255
  Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
---
Consider yourself to be nothing.
Completely forget yourself and
your troubles when you pray.
Pray only for Divine Presence,
Then you will enter a realm beyond time
where all separateness ceases to exist.
